From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: pai-nix <pai-nix@localhost>
Date: Thu, 11 Jun 2026 01:10:00 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 27/27] Remove ElevenLabs from the installer (key step, LIVE
 key-validation egress, voice picker)

Upstream issue: (pai-nix — sovereignty policy; no upstream issue.)

Part 2/3 of the vendor-TTS removal (0026 = runtime, 0028 = skills).
The install wizard was the LAST live vendor egress in the tree:
engine/detect.ts validateElevenLabsKey() POSTs the user's key to
api.elevenlabs.io/v1/voices, and generate-welcome.ts synthesizes the
welcome line through the vendor API. Both are gone, along with every
place the wizard finds, asks for, stores or reports a vendor key.

What changes:

  - engine/actions.ts — runVoiceSetup (~470 lines: key collection,
    key validation, vendor voice picker with preview synthesis, env
    writes) replaced by a no-op placeholder step that keeps step
    numbering, dependencies and resume state working; a local-TTS
    patch reactivates it. Key prefill from detection, the EL signals
    in the backup inventory, the ELEVENLABS_API_KEY env write in
    runConfiguration, and the vendor key import are removed.
  - engine/detect.ts — validateElevenLabsKey() deleted (the live
    egress); ELEVENLABS_API_KEY scan pattern + elevenLabsKeyFound out.
  - engine/validate.ts — "ElevenLabs API key" check removed (with the
    runtime de-vendored in 0026 a stored key would mean nothing);
    summary voiceMode is now "none".
  - engine/types.ts — elevenLabsKeyFound / apiKeys.elevenLabs /
    collected.elevenLabsKey fields and the "elevenlabs" voice_enabled
    mode removed. DEFAULT_VOICES/VoiceOption STAY (config-gen.ts
    writes daidentity.voices.main.voiceId from them) but are
    re-documented as legacy opaque ids for the local engine to map.
  - engine/steps.ts — step descriptions de-vendored (api-keys stays a
    passthrough; voice is a placeholder).
  - cli/display.ts, public/app.js, web/routes.ts — vendor key
    reporting lines and the unused validateElevenLabsKey import out.
  - generate-welcome.ts — deleted (standalone vendor TTS script).

Verified: anchor-checked substitutions + range-replace with over/
undershoot guards; rg -i 'elevenlabs|xi-api' clean across PAI-Install
code (README.md prose = documented residual); zero references to the
removed symbols; actions/validate/detect/steps/types/config-gen/routes
transpile (bun build), app.js passes node --check; the whole patch
series applies cleanly and nix build succeeds.

Known residual: PAI-Install/README.md prose (inert), DOCUMENTATION/
mentions (since 0026), skills recipes (until 0028).
